lyrics:
gululu gululu, let's go brush our teeth

Brush your teeth up and down

Clean along gaps with care
Cavities go buzz buzz away

Tooth by tooth ding ding hooray

Chorus:
Happily sing tra la la
Brush diligently everyday
Fight tooth decay
Smile bright, hip hip hooray

Verse 2:
Circle round those whites

Shoo away tiny bugs

Tooth by tooth make bright
Rinse and gargle after right

Chorus:

Happily sing tra la la
Brush diligently everyday
Fight tooth decay
Smile bright, hip hip hooray
